    Movie & TV Tours

    Vera Tour of Newcastle TV Locations

    5 reviews
    Discover the world of Detective Chief Inspector Vera Stanhope on a 4-hour tour around Northumberland. Listen to live commentary on board the coach as you visit shooting locations from the iconic television series including Gateshead, North Shields, and Whitley Bay. Enjoy time to explore Newcastle Castle, where you get free admission. The tour is a great opportunity to combine your love of history and your favorite TV inspector.
    $48.90 per adult

    Classy Cinema Experience
    Very nice cinema with friendly staff. Regular seats had plenty of leg room and seems like they have some nicer seating if you spend extra. The cinema itself shows its heritage which is a plus however I think this does impact the cinema experience with a below average sceensize cinemas and very average audio compared to some modern. If you are here for the bombastic side of cinema you may be a little disappointed. However this cinema does show many smaller films and events you will struggle find at large chains. If you are looking for a more relaxed cinema experience this is a perfect place. Looking for a feast of the senses? Might be worth considering other establishments.…

    77Sunny77 wrote a review Feb 2020
    UK57 contributions31 helpful votes
    Lovely Experience
    We really enjoyed our first visit here! We sat upstairs in the circle (front row) for a subtitled film which I was slightly worried about being able to see because of the balcony. I shouldnt have worried as it was absolutely fine and we could see the subtitles no problem in our comfy seats. In the stalls and circle you could buy some snacks / drinks / beers etc before the film. Everyone was really friendly. We booked online and received e-tickets so just skipped the queue on the way in and went straight upstairs. Theres lots of information on the walls upstairs telling you the history of the theatre which was interesting. Would definitely go back!…

I'd recommend this movie theatre to anyone wanting a true cinema experience!…
